ygData.subject: Re: Seinfeldisms
ygData.msgSnippet: I need to chill , I NEED TO CHILL (just kidding), no I am not upset either, i am just seeing a bad trend of people and thier opinions in and out of the
ygData.messageBody:
I need to "chill", I NEED TO "CHILL" (just kidding), no I am not upset
either, i am just seeing a bad trend of people and thier opinions in and out
of the game. People in this game are becoming rude for some reason or
another. I dont understand it but I really hope it changes. The worst I have
seen is on the new server. I putting it off as people just trying to get a
quick edge before everyone else but its been a week and things arent
changing, oh well.
